Please check and confirm in UAT Server.

Ticket Id
Project Name
Reported date

Description


E3251

Import Detention Slip
 Refer telecom on Saturday (1-Feb-2020), we require the detention calculation process for some specific customers in monthly basis for not returned containers (for return containers till the return date) . So, while calculating detention system will give

Body:
Dear Sushant Sir,


Required changes done for below scenario please find details on below and attached Test case for your ref.




If Vendor bill credit note done and same charge need to make another vendor bill please add it on OPS Additional charge and make sure that the charge Term should selected as "Only vendor bill".In OPS Additional charge screen provided charge Term "Only Vendor Bill" which can be used only for Vendor bill purpose.Above Term selected charge will not come for any invoice screen.This 'Only vendor Bill' Term will appear only for Vendor bill credit note processed Batch not for All.


Kindly check the same in UAT Server and confirm the status to Release it on live.
Subject: Re: REGARDING LINE PAYMENT OF OCEAN NETWORK CREDIT NOTE

Kindly check the same in UAT Server and confirm the status to Release it on live.
whole_body:
Dear Sushant Sir,

Required changes done for below scenario please find details on below and attached Test case for your ref.

If Vendor bill credit note done and same charge need to make another vendor bill please add it on OPS Additional charge and make sure that the charge Term should selected as "Only vendor bill".In OPS Additional charge screen provided charge Term "Only Vendor Bill" which can be used only for Vendor bill purpose.Above Term selected charge will not come for any invoice screen.This 'Only vendor Bill' Term will appear only for Vendor bill credit note processed Batch not for All.

Kindly check the same in UAT Server and confirm the status to Release it on live.

---------- Forwarded message ---------
From: <dayoutings@mamallaresort.com>
Date: Sat, Feb 1, 2020 at 3:31 PM
Subject: Mr. Bharath Day Get Together on 16th Feb 2020
To: <hr@ebms.co.in>
Cc: Krishnaraj <krishnaraj@mamallaresort.com>

Mamalla Beach Resort

small enough for privacy!
Big enough for comfort!!!!

Many Greetings from all of us in Mamalla Beach Resorts...!!!

Kind Attn.: Mr. Bharath,
9380565304

Dear Sir,
This is with reference to our telephone discussion regarding your corporate / family / friends get-together at our resort. We are very happy to post you the details for your reference:

Date: 16th Feb 2020

09:00 hrs.-
Welcome drink on arrival  A fresh fruit juice
13:00 hrs. - Lunch: with Four non veg. two deserts -
kindly find the file attach
16:00 hrs. - Tea / coffee with hot snacks
18:00 hrs. - Check out

We will entertain your delegates by providing enough number of tables, chairs, beach volleyballs, cricket kits, Frisbees, badminton racquets,
 rope for tug of war, etc.. at the beachfront.
The above said package would cost you Rs. 820/- net including taxes per head.

We discount the same package to
Rs. 735/- net including taxes per person for a minimum guarantee of
50 paying persons. The billing would be done based on this count.
Note: Children below 5 years are complimentary; children between the age of 5 & 12 years are chargeable at Rs. 500/- net per head.

Our price for use of the swimming pool facilities for two hours is
Rs.200/- net per head.
We further discount this to Rs. 160/- net per head. Children 5 to 12 years Rs. 80/- net per head.

Note: Mandatory swimming dress code - T- shirts & Bermuda's for women & swimming trunks for men. Swimming pool usage between 07:00 am and 06:00 pm. Pool usage strictly prohibited after consumption of alcohol.
 The arrangement of music system would cost you Rs.2500/- net.
 Special offer on A/c room for day-usage is available at Rs.3400/-. The normal tariff is of the room is Rs. 5587/- net.

For cocktails and liquor kindly use our bar facilities. All major brands of alcohol, beer, soda, soft drinks and snacks are available at special rates.
We do not permit outside liquor.
Kindly find the attach bar details for your reference:
We are equipped with a fully functional Ayurvethic spa.

We request you for a 50% advance payment while confirming your program.

The Advance payment Details:
You can deposit a cheque at any of the Axis Bank branch or ATM counter. Please do not deposit cash. Otherwise net bank fund transfer

AXIS BANK Ac/ No:
 9180 2007 0393 613
Account Name - Mamalla Beach Resort. CURRENT ACCOUNT
MICR CODE - 600211014 
IFSC CODE - UTIB0000423
Address: Axis Bank Ltd., Neelankarai Branch, Thiruvanmiyur, Chennai - 41.

Kindly feel free to call us for any assistance on +91 94426 46875

Looking forward to meeting you at our resort.

Rajeev Kannoth 

Manager
Marketing & Customer Relations

Mamalla Beach Resort,
108, Kovalam Road ( East Coast Road ),
Mamallapuram  603104
Tel: 044 - 2744 2475 / 3475, Mob: +91 94426 46875,
Fax: 044 - 2744 2875,
Mail: rajeev@mamallaresort.com
www.mamallaresort.com

-- 

Regards
Bharat
HR - Desk
eBMS Solutions Private Limited
(eNabling>>>eProductivity)
Chennai - Tamilnadu
